      <h1 class="blog-title">Does a New Bathroom Add Value to a Liverpool Property? The Numbers.</h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">A bathroom renovation is one of the highest-return home improvements available to Liverpool homeowners. Here is what the numbers actually show and what you should spend to maximise your return.</p>
      <div class="blog-meta">
        <span><strong>By</strong> Ideal Plumbing Solutions</span>
        <span><strong>Gas Safe Registered Engineers</strong></span>
        <span>December 2025</span>
        <span>5 min read</span>
      </div>
    </div>
